{"ELSE":[{"def":"Other; one or something beside; as, Who else is coming What else shall I give Do you expect anything else \"Bastards and else.","pos":""}],"ELSEWHERE":[{"def":"In any other place; as, these trees are not to be found elsewhere.","pos":""},{"def":"In some other place; in other places, indefinitely; as, it is reported in town and elsewhere.","pos":""}],"ELSEWHITHER":[{"def":"To some, or any, other place; as, you will have to go elsewhither for it.","pos":""}],"ELSIN":[{"def":"A shoemaker's awl.","pos":""}]}